    <p>The formulation in Equation (<xref ref-type="disp-formula" rid="M2">2</xref>) facilitates a generative interpretation by a factor analysis model with <italic>p</italic> factors (Everitt, <xref ref-type="bibr" rid="B9">1984</xref>)
