    <p><italic>Relation to Independent Component Analysis (ICA)</italic>: our models are closely related to ICA (Hyv√§rinen, <xref ref-type="bibr" rid="B20">1999</xref>). ICA searches for a matrix factorization, where the components of <inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="btq227i8.jpg"/></inline-formula> in model Equation (<xref ref-type="disp-formula" rid="M3">3</xref>) without noise <bold>Œµ</bold> should be mutually independent. The matrix decomposition for ICA is
