      <p>The data should be centered to zero mean, zero median or zero mode (<ext-link ext-link-type="uri" xlink:href="http://bioinformatics.oxfordjournals.org/cgi/content/full/btq227/DC1">Supplementary Material</ext-link>). If the correlation of weak signals is of interest too, we recommend to normalize the data.</p>
